Class ParametrizedDatatypeImpl

java.lang.Object

      org.hl7.meta.impl.ParametrizedDatatypeImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, Datatype, Metadata, ParametrizedDatatype
public class ParametrizedDatatypeImpl
extends DatatypeImpl
implements ParametrizedDatatype

Generic data type with one parameter, e.g. LIST<TEL> or UVP<CD>, IVL<TS>.

Author:
Skirmantas Kligys, modified by Gunther Schadow, Eric Chen

I unified the versions with 1 or 2 parameters to one with n parameters. this reduces the number of special cases.
